{"tid":1475333,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"解散軍放核彈，求拆彈！！拆唔掂個運動就會完架啦！","createTime":"2019-08-15T12:30:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T14:53:03.000Z","uid":190927,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"db1cdfe60ccd791e8e9e0a4aa99f77f04e358ddf","tid":1475333,"uid":190927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T12:30:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">極危險，對家準備在輿論戰放核彈！所有非前線人員準備迎擊！有人打算挾和理非民意打散我地！！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n尋日係港豬親戚收到條google 問卷的link，click入去第一段就話收集和理非意見，希望未來的行動有所改善，仲話不記名調查，放心填，幾咁漂亮多麼的善意。<br />\n<br />\n碌落去第一頁好似冇乜野，去到第八題：點解一定要在＂公義丶經濟丶民生＂之中三揀二呢？係咪有伏味呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/09Vp0Ui.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F09Vp0Ui.jpg&h=cc728725&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m80ab0Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm80ab0Z.jpg&h=8955f185&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到第二頁係列舉不同情況，不斷問人支唔支持(＝割不割蓆)（9至16題），用字充滿誘導性，潛臺詞洗腦割蓆，意志稍微不夠堅定，很易上當，所以我做既時候都填左「標準答案」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Pccqmc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Pccqmc.jpg&h=6ab5627c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aHU2Nzy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaHU2Nzy.jpg&h=21ddb363&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DcdnNzz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDcdnNzz.jpg&h=4f0a63eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VAaxqmf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVAaxqmf.jpg&h=bf59ce65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/12wgR1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F12wgR1f.jpg&h=bf508966&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同IT朋友商量過，其實只要你開條link，因為digital footprint，問卷發起人係可能會有辦法揾到你。佢地唔洗知你係邊個，佢地更重視人同人的網絡，因為spread 晒和理非之間就得，所以其實非常惡劣。除左不斷潛臺詞洗腦割蓆，得到數據可以挾民意來攻擊前線抗爭者。我原本問IT朋友有沒有辦法可以靜靜地令發起人消失，技術上除左人海檢舉佢之外基本沒方法。但若果要吹雞叫人，就代表很多人會看到問卷，也非我所願。況且就算port爆佢，佢都可以撕一貼十，google doc仲低成本過連儂牆。其實我都有諗過吹雞叫人填支持勇武，但佢一個人/成個團隊有數據就可以隨意詮譯，所以我都係填完就算。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當我仲猶疑緊要點處理既時候，今天就見到陸續有假聯署。然後當大家都嘲笑假聯署充滿破綻果時，我就越覺得份google 問卷有惡意但又無乜破綻，真係極危險。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">所以我決定都係要講出黎！</span><br />\n<br />\n想話去cap返完整的圖，人地已經close左又close埋右，我宜家唔敢想象佢會公布啲咩，喺邊度公佈。<br />\n<br />\n集思廣益，可以點樣同啲人打定預防針？仲可以點樣唔俾人帶風向？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f7401a2b8adc916686284c79d06d3a23f99a59f","tid":1475333,"uid":190927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T12:31:00.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"2bcfa7bc118cceec56d95da28849c27824fc8292","tid":1475333,"uid":190927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T12:31:46.000Z","msg":"原lin <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdHYhY4EBHn4PFMD3DyIUVYxT1QKqLe6jQ-NHKivT9MWMzX5g/closedform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdHYhY4EBHn4PFMD3DyIUVYxT1QKqLe6jQ-NHKivT9MWMzX5g%2Fclosedform&d=LSsgDEuqvL%2F6lC7PehFbgx%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=c4367727\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdHYhY4EBHn4PFMD3DyIUVYxT1QKqLe6jQ-NHKivT9MWMzX5g/closedform</a>"},{"pid":"7ce6f0f4c15f522b7a1a59f872648f2b1bdd2f6e","tid":1475333,"uid":190927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re